title: Inter-Parliamentary Union Adopts Statement Against Sanctions on Lawmakers
text: The Governing Council of the Inter-Parliamentary Union on Sunday adopted a statement on inadmissibility of sanctions against lawmakers, Chairman of Russia's Federation Council Committee on Foreign Affairs Konstantin Kosachev said. ...
